html
  body
    head
      meta(charset='utf-8')
      meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
      meta(name='description' content='ldap-authentication testing')
      meta(name='author' content='Jingshao Chen')
      link(rel='stylesheet' href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css' integrity='sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm' crossorigin='anonymous')
      title Testing Page to use ldap-authentication as a passport strategy
      
    .container.d-flex.h-100.align-items-center.justify-content-center
      div
        .row.justify-content-center
          h1.text-center Use ldap-authentication as a passport strategy
        .row.justify-content-center
          .col-sm-4
            form(action='/login' method='post')
              h1.h3.mb-3.font-weight-normal.text-center Sign in
              p
                | Use 
                code gauss
                |  and 
                code password
                |  to test.
              .form-label-group
                input#username.form-control.rounded-0(name='username' type='text' autocomplete='username' placeholder='Username' required='' autofocus='')
              .form-label-group
                input#password.form-control.rounded-0(name='password' type='password' autocomplete='current-password' placeholder='Password' required='')
              div
                input.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-block.rounded-0.mt-3(type='submit')
        .row.justify-content-center
          p.text-muted.text-center.small
            | Online LDAP test server provided by 
            a(href='https://www.forumsys.com/tutorials/integration-how-to/ldap/online-ldap-test-server/') forumsys